name: Ical-event-creator-app
tagline: Repository for the iCal Event Creator App
body:
### Welcome to iCal-Event-Creator-App



The project aims to allow for a GUI interface that can create .ics files with various specifications that most iCal calendars are unable to do including multi-day events and GPS location.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
